OL,3,CHull City promoted to Premier League
OL,4,Cafter stoppage-time winner
OL,6,FHull City will play in England's top
OL,7,Ftier for the first time in nine years
OL,8,Fafter beating Middlesbrough 1-0 in the
OL,9,FEFL Championship play-off final.
OL,11,FTemperatures of 28 degrees greeted the
OL,12,Fplayers as they graced the Wembley
OL,13,Fturf for a fixture that has dominated
OL,14,Fthe headlines for more than sporting
OL,15,Freasons alone.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
