CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779559869
OL,3,CHull City promoted to Premier League
OL,4,Cafter stoppage-time winner
OL,6,FIn a tight first half where
OL,7,FMiddlesbrough had the edge, Hull's
OL,8,Ftalismanic number nine Oli McBurnie
OL,9,Fcame closest to opening the scoring,
OL,10,Fhitting the crossbar with a header
OL,11,Fjust before the break.
OL,13,FAfter another energy sapping second
OL,14,Fhalf in the heat, it was McBurnie
OL,15,Fagain who pounced after Yu Hirakawa's
OL,16,Fcross was parried by the Middlesbrough
OL,17,Fkeeper.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
