PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779559869
OL,3,CHull City promoted to Premier League
OL,4,Cafter stoppage-time winner
OL,6,FHaving finished sixth in the regular
OL,7,Fseason, it is the first time in seven
OL,8,Fyears that neither the 3rd nor 4th-
OL,9,Fplaced team in the play-offs has won
OL,10,Fpromotion.
OL,12,FPromotion to the Premier League comes
OL,13,Fwith a financial windfall and an
OL,14,Festimated additional revenue of at
OL,15,Fleast #200m, much needed amid the
OL,16,Fbackdrop of a transfer embargo and
OL,17,Floses totalling more than #40m in
OL,18,Frecent accounts.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779559869
OL,3,CHull City promoted to Premier League
OL,4,Cafter stoppage-time winner
OL,6,FThere had been doubt as to whether the
OL,7,Fmatch would go ahead on the date
OL,8,Foriginally scheduled after City's
OL,9,Foriginal opponents Southampton were
OL,10,Fembroiled in what has become the
OL,11,Fseason's most notorious off-field
OL,12,Fdrama, dubbed "Spygate".
OL,14,FSouthampton admitted to spying on a
OL,15,Ftraining session held by Middlesbrough
OL,16,Fahead of their play-off semi-final, as
OL,17,Fwell as sessions held by Oxford United
OL,18,Fin December and Ipswich Town session
OL,19,Fin April.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779559869
OL,3,CHull City promoted to Premier League
OL,4,Cafter stoppage-time winner
OL,6,FHaving been ejected from the play-off
OL,7,Ffinal in favour of Middlesbrough and
OL,8,Fseeing their subsequent appeal
OL,9,Frejected, the FA confirmed the club
OL,10,Fwill be investigated.
OL,12,FIn an interview with Calendar earlier
OL,13,Fin the week, Tigers owner Acun Ilicali
OL,14,Fsaid the controversy had
OL,15,F"overshadowed" Hull's achievement in
OL,16,Fbeating Millwall to make the final.
OL,18,FMr Ilicali also called on the EFL not
OL,19,Fto "spoil our beautiful fans'
OL,20,Fbeautiful day".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
