PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779559869
OL,3,CHull City promoted to Premier League
OL,4,Cafter stoppage-time winner
OL,6,FPrior to the game Hull's captain Lewie
OL,7,FCoyle had said he hoped to win to
OL,8,Fhonour his late father.
OL,10,FChris Coyle was a well-known figure in
OL,11,Fthe city, having run a long-
OL,12,Festablished fruit and veg stall before
OL,13,Fhis sudden death in June 2022.
OL,15,FCoyle said: "He'd be proud. I want to
OL,16,Fshare this with him, wherever he is,
OL,17,Fif he is looking down. I'm sure he is.
OL,18,FThat's what I sort of cling onto."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
