CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779559869
OL,3,CHull City promoted to Premier League
OL,4,Cafter stoppage-time winner
OL,6,FIt was not Hull's first taste of
OL,7,Fsuccess in the Championship play-off
OL,8,Ffinal, finding comfort at Wembley
OL,9,Fhaving won on three of their four
OL,10,Fvisits.
OL,12,FThe Tigers won thanks to an incredible
OL,13,FDean Windass volley in 2008, while
OL,14,Fit's ten years since Mo Diame's strike
OL,15,Fsaw off Sheffield Wednesday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
